        &lt;p&gt;
Smoketest scripts exist for exactly this in ckanext. It would be great to have this running on nagios.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
It is as simple as running:
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
python blackbox/smoke.py -H ckan.net blackbox/ckan.net.profile.json
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
See here for code:
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;a class="ext-link" href="https://bitbucket.org/okfn/ckanext/src/default/blackbox"&gt;&lt;span class="icon"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;https://bitbucket.org/okfn/ckanext/src/default/blackbox&lt;/a&gt;
